# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ZMarketVN - Environment Variables Guide
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development
# Set these in Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables for production
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ─── 1. DATABASE (PostgreSQL - REQUIRED for Vercel) ─────────────────────────
# Vercel không hỗ trợ SQLite! Phải dùng PostgreSQL.
# Đăng ký miễn phí tại: https://neon.tech (Free 0.5GB, serverless)
#
# Ví dụ: postgresql://neondb_owner:AbCdEf@ep-cool-name-123456.us-east-1.aws.neon.tech/neondb?sslmode=require
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@host:5432/database?sslmode=require"

# Local development (SQLite - chỉ dùng khi dev local, KHÔNG dùng cho Vercel):
# DATABASE_URL="file:./dev.db"

# ─── 2. COOKIE SECRET (BẮT BUỘC) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Dùng để ký cookie xác thực. Tạo random: openssl rand -base64 48
COOKIE_SECRET=your-random-secret-key-at-least-32-characters-long

# ─── 3. CLOUDINARY - Upload ảnh (BẮT BUỘC cho Vercel) ──────────────────────
# Đăng ký miễn phí tại: https://cloudinary.com (25GB free!)
# Sau khi đăng ký, vào Dashboard → Copy 3 giá trị:
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your-cloud-name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=123456789012345
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your-api-secret-here

# ─── 4. GOOGLE OAUTH (TÙY CHỌN - có thể bỏ qua) ────────────────────────────
# Cần thiết lập tại: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# Authorized redirect URI: https://your-app.vercel.app/api/auth/google
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID.apps.googleusercontent.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=YOUR_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET
GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:3000/api/auth/google

# ─── 5. REALTIME SERVICE (Pusher Channels - REQUIRED for Chat) ──────────────
# Đăng ký tài khoản miễn phí tại: https://pusher.com
PUSHER_APP_ID="your-pusher-app-id"
PUSHER_KEY="your-pusher-key"
PUSHER_SECRET="your-pusher-secret"
PUSHER_CLUSTER="ap1"

# Client-side (Public) keys:
NEXT_PUBLIC_PUSHER_KEY="your-pusher-key"
NEXT_PUBLIC_PUSHER_CLUSTER="ap1"

# Local: http://localhost:3000
# Vercel: https://your-app.vercel.app
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000

# ─── 7. VNPAY SANDBOX (Tích hợp thanh toán) ──────────────────────────────────
VNP_TMN_CODE="your-vnpay-tmn-code"
VNP_HASH_SECRET="your-vnpay-hash-secret"
VNP_URL="https://sandbox.vnpayment.vn/paymentv2/vpcpay.html"
VNP_RETURN_URL="http://localhost:3000/thanh-toan/ket-qua"
VNP_IPN_URL="http://localhost:3000/api/payment/webhook/vnpay"
